我當天那位置<br />\n情外情 轉了對象 別要太驚訝<br />\n⋯⋯⋯⋯⋯⋯⋯⋯⋯⋯⋯⋯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咁我又冇絲打你咁灰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n大家都係想爭取D 想要既野姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n佢地一齊左幾耐 因為鐘意左你所以散？</blockquote><br />\n佢地一齊大半年 男方因為呷醋同女方鬧交 大家冇搵大家 半個月之後男方主動提出頂唔順分手<br />\n我係佢地鬧交果陣先識呢個女仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 完全無諗咩乘唔乘虛而入 應該唔關我事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3ac2b8acafb6dd835921905de3c0752eaaabd10d","tid":322442,"uid":26675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-14T21:27:52.000Z","msg":"我係穩陣派既<br />\n觀察一段時間先開始, 起碼有段時間去cool down 比相方去思考依段關係<br />\n唔洗驚friend 唔friend zone 問題, 如果係一齊終會一齊到<br />\n諗清楚先行, 唔好比當時既感性去主宰你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"db4f64bc1ea44c7ccb92d4960cea017212ac6085","tid":322442,"uid":22248,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-14T21:31:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我係穩陣派既<br />\n觀察一段時間先開始, 起碼有段時間去cool down 比相方去思考依段關係<br />\n唔洗驚friend 唔friend zone 問題, 如果係一齊終會一齊到<br />\n諗清楚先行, 唔好比當時既感性去主宰你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n可能我真係一個太感性行先既人<br />\n一日流流長成日都會諗呢d 野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我會記住巴打你講過呢段說話<br />\n事實上都有唔少人咁樣同我講過<br />\n我只可以盡量控制下自己 擺返D 注意力去其他野度<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fc7a1050528b005441ee4ab0e5ca22e6e7267cad","tid":322442,"uid":37648,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-14T21:38:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>佢鍾唔鍾意你先？<br />\n鍾意你既就算岩岩分手需要啲時間都未必會咁樣避 會淨係同你講佢要啲時間 或者唔好chur佢住先<br />\n同埋岩岩散就一齊好易做水泡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n係我地有情侶行為之前佢自己暗示過有好感<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 所以先敢去馬 當時所有野都好自然咁發生左<br />\n我又冇乜特別諗咩水唔水泡果D<br />\n<br />\n有時矛盾既係唔chur 佢 D 話題就只會越黎越日常 平凡到連我自己都唔似覺得係追緊佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但係chur 完得返黎既response係咁冷淡既話 或者老友你都講得岩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 不過老老實實我同你經歷緊幾乎同一樣野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔同既係 佢同佢男朋友一齊果陣已經話鍾意我<br />\n跟住都係拖攬錫做齊 不過前排佢想同佢男朋友分手果陣又唔係幾捨得幾年感情<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但佢仲係鍾意我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 所以而家我都係見步行步算 唔敢有希望<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nBTW，佢會唔會係之後諗清楚唔想咁樣/唔再鍾意你？"},{"pid":"50d76121128bb2af567c72863db428da67fe3cb9","tid":322442,"uid":56141,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-14T21:45:11.000Z","msg":"我個時分手一排都好有陰影好驚再拍拖<br />\n又驚會當左男朋友係水泡 咁會對佢唔好<br />\n好彩個時男朋友冇嫌棄我 <br />\n又比好多心機同我傾計 <br />\n仲話明知都陪我慢慢行一齊行<br />\n而家雖然仲努力放低緊ex <br />\n但個時真係鐘意會比佢打動到 <br />\n唔會拖攬錫做齊但又避佢🤔<br />\n<br />\n利申藍絲"},{"pid":"3a94faa33b2f68d691317e8fbbc2d3e86958e598","tid":322442,"uid":22248,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-14T21:45:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 不過老老實實我同你經歷緊幾乎同一樣野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔同既係 佢同佢男朋友一齊果陣已經話鍾意我<br />\n跟住都係拖攬錫做齊 不過前排佢想同佢男朋友分手果陣又唔係幾捨得幾年感情<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但佢仲係鍾意我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 所以而家我都係見步行步算 唔敢有希望<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nBTW，佢會唔會係之後諗清楚唔想咁樣/唔再鍾意你？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n聽完覺得巴打仲慘過我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好似比人逢場作戲咁<br />\n真心仲hurt 過想追一個女仔又追唔到<br />\n<br />\n唔想有情侶行為係肯定既 至少而家已經冇曬<br />\n<br />\n至於唔再鍾意我？呢個我都答唔到你<br />\n一黎好似上面咁講 平時打字D 訊息都冇乜味道可言<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但係有時會feel 到佢又幾著緊我 例如會講下話我夜晚唔煩住佢唔慣 會知我通左頂買野比我食<br />\n我話買早餐佢食 送佢返屋企果D 佢都受<br />\n但其實朋友之間都會做呢D 野？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"62f32103653b779828dfa254edd49c84b98c888d","tid":322442,"uid":62964,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-14T21:46:54.000Z","msg":"條女咁既性格你都肯濟<br />\n拍緊拖仲同人搞三搞四<br />\n不過樓主都唔好得去邊<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9a4dd57e60778032f951332b1fb19299ca7b3ed6","tid":322442,"uid":22248,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-14T21:50:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我個時分手一排都好有陰影好驚再拍拖<br />\n又驚會當左男朋友係水泡 咁會對佢唔好<br />\n好彩個時男朋友冇嫌棄我 <br />\n又比好多心機同我傾計 <br />\n仲話明知都陪我慢慢行一齊行<br />\n而家雖然仲努力放低緊ex <br />\n但個時真係鐘意會比佢打動到 <br />\n唔會拖攬錫做齊但又避佢🤔<br />\n<br />\n利申藍絲</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n可能真係太快，其實我個故事，由佢鬧交，識到佢，佢散，再同我曖昧，到煞車，到而家只係一個幾月既事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9d0e5baacdaa0fb986124fdc4f82da5a59ff617f","tid":322442,"uid":22248,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-14T21:53:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>條女咁既性格你都肯濟<br />\n拍緊拖仲同人搞三搞四<br />\n不過樓主都唔好得去邊<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n最岩聽最尾果句<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不嬲好唔鍾意唔嗲唔吊又懦弱既自己<br />\n<br />\n呷醋果單野其實極少事 係個男仔自己太小器太敏感<br />\n再加上有人對男方加鹽加醋（大概係唔抵得個女仔有拖拍所以煽風點火，offtopic 女人既嫉妒心真係好可怕）<br />\n先會搞到佢地咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"738f5f38cb2908c0f2bc46d5b698184e013488b9","tid":322442,"uid":56141,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-14T21:55:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>我個時分手一排都好有陰影好驚再拍拖<br />\n又驚會當左男朋友係水泡 咁會對佢唔好<br />\n好彩個時男朋友冇嫌棄我 <br />\n又比好多心機同我傾計 <br />\n仲話明知都陪我慢慢行一齊行<br />\n而家雖然仲努力放低緊ex <br />\n但個時真係鐘意會比佢打動到 <br />\n唔會拖攬錫做齊但又避佢🤔<br />\n<br />\n利申藍絲</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n可能真係太快，其實我個故事，由佢鬧交，識到佢，佢散，再同我曖昧，到煞車，到而家只係一個幾月既事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咁又快左啲好似<br />\n個時我散左兩個月 識左現任<br />\n第三個月一齊 個時都仲有諗會唔會太快 <br />\n驚太兒戲對佢唔好咁 <br />\n依家就散左都半年有多 仲努力放低緊 <br />\n同時都努力比緊信心男朋友 <br />\n咁可能你都要比啲時間佢"},{"pid":"16c530745ba486ebdb94a1f1ca4afd11d3988e5a","tid":322442,"uid":22248,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-14T22:05:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>我個時分手一排都好有陰影好驚再拍拖<br />\n又驚會當左男朋友係水泡 咁會對佢唔好<br />\n好彩個時男朋友冇嫌棄我 <br />\n又比好多心機同我傾計 <br />\n仲話明知都陪我慢慢行一齊行<br />\n而家雖然仲努力放低緊ex <br />\n但個時真係鐘意會比佢打動到 <br />\n唔會拖攬錫做齊但又避佢🤔<br />\n<br />\n利申藍絲</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n可能真係太快，其實我個故事，由佢鬧交，識到佢，佢散，再同我曖昧，到煞車，到而家只係一個幾月既事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咁又快左啲好似<br />\n個時我散左兩個月 識左現任<br />\n第三個月一齊 個時都仲有諗會唔會太快 <br />\n驚太兒戲對佢唔好咁 <br />\n依家就散左都半年有多 仲努力放低緊 <br />\n同時都努力比緊信心男朋友 <br />\n咁可能你都要比啲時間佢</blockquote><br />\n本身都唔係想咁快但一切發生得太自然<br />\n快到我自己都覺得有情侶行為果幾日完全唔似拍拖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f1960bde086f9b0f1da842815f607368e5105b41","tid":322442,"uid":6347,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-14T22:10:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>比d刺激佢</blockquote><br />\n咩意思<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n諗下點樣令佢對住你會有坐過山車果陣既感覺<br />\n唔係就等收皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/29.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6191953a1b0e27020e24bfa1d9205f7522e77de9","tid":322442,"uid":28943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-14T22:13:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>當初喜歡你 其時你有別人<br />\n完全都因為我 才完結過去拋低了他<br />\n下個他 不過接替我當天那位置<br />\n情外情 轉了對象 別要太驚訝<br />\n⋯⋯⋯⋯⋯⋯⋯⋯⋯⋯⋯⋯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咁我又冇絲打你咁灰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n大家都係想爭取D 想要既野姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n佢地一齊左幾耐 因為鐘意左你所以散？</blockquote><br />\n佢地一齊大半年 男方因為呷醋同女方鬧交 大家冇搵大家 半個月之後男方主動提出頂唔順分手<br />\n我係佢地鬧交果陣先識呢個女仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 完全無諗咩乘唔乘虛而入 應該唔關我事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n點解明知人地有男朋友 又鬧緊交果陣先去識人？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead